<h2>FAQ</h2>

<h3>Is there a sign-up or email required?</h3>
<p>No. Your wallet address is your account. Connect and start using immediately.</p>

<h3>Does signing the message cost gas?</h3>
<p>No. The sign-in message is off-chain — it proves wallet ownership without any transaction.</p>

<h3>Is my data shared with other users?</h3>
<p>No. All data is isolated per wallet. Your watchlists, portfolios, and chat history are private.</p>

<h3>What market data is available?</h3>
<p>Qwenta provides real-time stock market data including OHLCV, RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands, SMA 20/50, and EMA 20.</p>

